Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, go right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluffy, fluffy, fluffy, fluffy, fluffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.29,0:00:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yffulf, yffulf, yffulf, yffulf, yffulf...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now back to the right. Ready? Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluffy, fluffy, fluffy, fluffy, fluffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Scarfs are warm, but they feel\Nso prickly on my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.61,0:00:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time we do these fluffy exercises,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,let's not do them with the scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's this stuff coming from your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I'm not quite sure, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...? Then I shall solve this mystery for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.88,0:00:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you're up to the task, Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't test me! I got a hundred\Non my science test before!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oho... Then I shall give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow... Now, Little. Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You go like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.99,0:01:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You must solve the mystery\Nin order to free your finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I'm gonna solve this in a jiffy\Nand get rid of this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, Yachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, who is this Yachi you speak of?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcoming the New Year by studying...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When did I become such an honor student?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:11.63,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Are you awake?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Yeah, I'm awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:23.01,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Can I call you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Sure, you can call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare for you to call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So, was this some kind of emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...wanted to give you a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you watching TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what kind of answer is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This year's almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you doing anything for New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We basically just go to my grandparents' place\Nfor a bit, but that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get New Year's money?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I guess I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura? Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I was just remembering your thighs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! M-My thighs...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, really? I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Well, you just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that sexual harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That wasn't sexual harassment.\NThat was a totally normal thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why my thighs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking how nice\Nyour lap pillow was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, because I'm lying down right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you prefer me\Nto make them harder or softer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My thighs. Which would you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they're fine just the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best not to gain weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You should probably worry about\Nnot losing too much weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I'm drinking that tea. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...using that thing all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we do New Year greetings?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep hanging out this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"Goodnight" sounds nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Sounds nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she just want to wish me a Happy New Year?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:07:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to be like, your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That shouldn't be too hard. I mean,\NI don't have that many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I sorta really want to be that, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I told her she already was,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think it'd make her happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because even if the phrase "best friend"\Nmay sound the same when we say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,there might be a difference in our\Nactual definition of the phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The level that Adachi wants\Nto take this relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,was so impossibly high that I'd probably\Nneed to sprout wings to even attain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to work harder this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I say that and then immediately do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think how I feel about Shimamura's chest\Nwill basically determine things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly I want from Shimamura
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,should be determined there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I want to see Shimamura's chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess... I can't say I don't want to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wouldn't say I'd particularly\Npursue this venture, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, so it's pretty normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My feelings for Shimamura are pure,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and I like Shimamura as a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, I love "Goodnight."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There shouldn't be an issue if I dove\Ninto Shimamura's bosom right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm completely normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Her face? Her chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, wait... That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:10:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what they mean by the biter gets bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think "digging my own grave"\Nis more fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't separate my struggles\Nfrom Shimamura just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when I was thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that my dye job was beginning to fade,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it's now February.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.62,0:10:25.87,On Top,,0,0,0,,"2/4 (Tues)"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Winter break had ended,\Nwe got new seating assignments,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was finally getting used to\Nsaid seating assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,January was over in a blink of an eye,\Nand now it's February.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As usual, Adachi seems to be acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Adachi's always acting weird, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,When our eyes meet, she looks away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to ask if she wants to hang out\Nand she ends up running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure that these past few days,\NI haven't even heard her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:11:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does she have to be such a troublemaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey. Hey, yo, Shima! I'm Hino!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't Hawaii and winter break\Nended a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't actually need anything. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she throwing that thing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What else would I be talking about?\NYou know, the boomerang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Yeah, I'm sure, uh,\Nmy little sister is throwing it around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her I challenge her to a duel\Nonce she gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you free today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere far away... Wait, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you wanted to\Nstop by someplace after school...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want to go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, we don't have to if you're busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, that's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm so insanely busy today...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Of course, I'm not busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to rub that in, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was lying when I said I was busy.\NSo let's go somewhere. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you have somewhere in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not anywhere exact, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"But"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um... I think I want some snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So Miss Adachi would like some sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:13:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, yup... Snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you prefer something not sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, er... Something sweet is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my hand. Here. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we're going to have something sweet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a donut shop right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:13:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you prefer Japanese sweets, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant. I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have somewhere in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh... No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I wanted to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I dye my hair again or go back to black?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure because I've never\Nseen you with black hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I am the purest little\NSnow White you'll find.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. My hair's starting to grow out,\Nso I was wondering what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:09.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Freshly Made Cream Puffs"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What about here? We can get takeout\Nand eat on the bench.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, uh, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:25.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Heart {\i1}Chocolat{\i0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.55,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Valentine's Day Fair"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I try lifting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Lifting what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I think I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:45.07,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Nagafuji Butcher Shop"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm floating! I'm floating! Wait... Ow, ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:16:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, my armpits hurt! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You were heavier than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, how rude can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what exactly were you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. I just figured I could lift you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you want chocolate this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I love sweet things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alrighty. I guess I'll buy you\Nsomething again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:32.36,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Valentine's Day Fair"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Valentine's... It says Valentine's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I... guess it's that time of year...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Valentine's?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not... a big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.18,0:17:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Adachi bring me here just to\Nshow me this Valentine's poster?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I guess I should just say that was\Na rather roundabout way of doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any plans on the 14th, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:18:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If you don't, could we hang out\Non the 14th, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Do you want chocolate or do you\Nwant to give me chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I mean, either. Or rather, let's exchange!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, friendship chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure Hino and Nagafuji\Ndo something like that every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't see this going\Nas smoothly as it'd go for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been doing this for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't the point to give someone chocolate\Nsuddenly that day as a surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how many years I'll be around Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe just until graduation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, once we move up a year,\Nwe might end up in different classes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and that might be the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's actually some hope\Nknowing it might happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There're still plenty of problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi was trying to take a step out\Nof the flow of our day-to-day life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but think
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that whatever direction she's taking,\Nit's always facing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't help but admire\Nher determination and resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Let's do Valentine's Day this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, every day just seemed grey and endless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But on this day, February 4th,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and the next ten days of grey,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,seemed to slowly have color added to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, working hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.64,0:22:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Getting side dishes for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.02,0:22:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.02,0:22:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, today, I'll get...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.19,0:22:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.62,0:22:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tarumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's me! It's been forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You sorta became really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.21,0:23:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Was "sorta" necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.58,0:23:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.13,0:23:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get your number?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.19,0:23:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagafuji had witnessed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.02,0:23:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Much lower key than a housewife\Nwitnessing something, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.07,0:23:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a call when I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.12,0:23:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.12,0:23:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.09,0:23:52.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 7: 'Please Choose\Nthe Best Chocolate for Me'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.59,0:23:52.09,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Tarumi"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.09,0:24:07.08,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Next Time: 'The Briar That\NWeaves the Past: Old Rose'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.05,0:23:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? Nagafuji in the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.06,0:23:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, check it out! Hino here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.56,0:24:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You went overseas for New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.56,0:24:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes! Souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.35,0:24:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Had to get the ol' chocolate-covered\Nmacadamia nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.73,0:24:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit your complainin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.90,0:24:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
